channel.title: My server is screwed up a bit
channel.description:
Ok. I added some things to my server, compile, no errors. Then, I go to runserver and I lo on and then I just lag out. It says I am already online, and does the same with every other account which tries to log on... any ideas... this is what I get...
[code]Starting Relm Of Dunes Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NumberFormatException: For input string: "0 662 " at java.lang.NumberFormatException.forInputString(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at java.lang.Integer.parseInt(Unknown Source) at NPCHandler.loadAutoSpawn(NPCHandler.java:1416) at NPCHandler.<init>(NPCHandler.java:23) at server.main(server.java:27)
[/code]
